<div xmlns:jsp="http://java.sun.com/JSP/Page" xmlns:c="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core" xmlns:roo="urn:jsptagdir:/WEB-INF/tags" xmlns:fmt="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt" xmlns:form="http://www.springframework.org/tags/form" xmlns:spring="http://www.springframework.org/tags">
    <h1>Forgot Password</h1>
    <p>If you were in our database we sent you an email with a new password.</p>
    <c:url value="/researcher/forgotPassword/form" var="forgotPassword" />
    <c:url value="/contact" var="contact"/>
    <p>If you do not receive this email you can check your spam filter, <a href="${forgotPassword}">try again</a> and if that doesn't work, <a href="${contact}">contact us</a>.</p>
</div>